abstract: Brett Stegmaier leads in second round at Shriners Hospitals for Children Open before play is suspended for darkness.
lead_paragraph: Brett Stegmaier led the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas in only his fifth career start on the PGA Tour.
